DIR
  AID
"Utilities for continuous Markov Chains
Dih5
*****
Magnitudes:
Q: Infinitesimal matrix
J: Jump matrix
Xj: j-th column of X
*****
Functions included:
X2Y: Function transforming X to Y
STATIO: Find a base of stationary distributions from Q
DIM1: Number of rows in a Matrix"
  Q2J
  ´ ç q
    ´ q DUP DIM1 ç q
d
      ´ 1 d
        FOR k q çROW
çLIST k GET DUP k GET
NEG DUP
          IF 0 ==
          THEN DROP
DIM1 1 SWAP
            FOR k2 0
            NEXT q
DIM1 çARRY k 1 PUT
          ELSE / k 0
PUT
          END
        NEXT d ROWç
      ª
    ª
  ª
  STATIO
  ´ TRAN KER 1
    ´ DUP OBJç 1 GET
çLIST ÖLIST EXPAND /
    ª DOLIST
  ª
  DIM1
  ´ SIZE 1 GET çQ
  ª
END
